### Political API Integration Tests

# Health Check
GET http://localhost:5014/health

###

# Set Political Position
POST http://localhost:5014/definir_posicao_politica
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usuario": "123456789",
  "x": -2.13,
  "y": -1.95
}

###

# Set Another Political Position
POST http://localhost:5014/definir_posicao_politica
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usuario": "987654321",
  "x": 3.5,
  "y": 4.2
}

###

# Get Political Position by User
GET http://localhost:5014/ver_posicao_politica/123456789

###

# Get All Political Positions (Graph Data)
GET http://localhost:5014/grafico_politico

###

